打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypycyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9100032c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1b0c7b177f8fca5f96f47439429a44cdf621a854","tid":1231784,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"今日熱身姐，71應該會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d1c96c63ef6cb520a59b41afdeb2fc42c47f8f","tid":1231784,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"吾出既都可以幫忙推有用既post同防止假消息流傳，每一個人都可以做出貢獻"}]}